			<h1>Not Just Little Adults: Policies to Support Medical Home Transformation in Pediatric Practice</h1>
			<p class="byline">By: David Keller, MD, Sara Toomey, MD, Jean Raphael, MD, MPH, Matthew Sadof, MD, Christopher Stille, MD, MPH</p>
		</div><!-- /.content-header-meta -->

