				<h3 class='comment-date'>Submitted 04/11/2014</h3>
				<div class='comment-main'>
					<div class='comment-content'><p>I agree with the article, but find it very difficult to keep the vision before the practice/physician to transform to PCMH when payment reform seems so distance (or non-existent). It also seems like the government wants to change things all the time so no one knows who/what is on first. I think we need to see payment for the changes discussed above OR we will NOT see the outcomes with PCMH we would like to see.</p></div>
					<p class='comment-author'>Pamela Ballou-Nelson, PhD</p>
